const WorkHistory = () => { return(

Work History

  • Undergraduate research assistant
    • Clemson University
    • February 2017 - August 2017
    • Worked on development of a stochastic model for generation of synthetic eye movements using real world data.
  • Graduate Teaching Assistant
    • Clemson University
    • August 2017 - December 2017
    • Teaching assistant for CPSC 4120/6120 Eye Tracking Methodologies.
  • Software Engineer
    • Getronics
    • January 2018 - February 2019
    • Worked as 4690OS P.O.S. for multiple large grocery chains.
  • Firmware Engineer
    • Itron
    • February 2019 - Present
    • Working as an embedded linux staff firmware engineer for the OpenWay Riva CENTRON Meter line of products.
); } export default WorkHistory;
